cs.IT, cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.MM

The paper discusses the security issues in wireless information and power transfer, which involves information theory (cs.IT), cryptography (cs.CR), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), systems and control (cs.SY), and multimedia (cs.MM). The focus on physical layer security techniques and massive MIMO also suggests a strong connection to information theory and systems and control. Therefore, cs.IT and cs.SY are the most likely categories, followed by cs.CR, cs.NI, and cs.MM.
